data.description: This stunning townhome, located in a prime and convenient location, offers 3 spacious bedrooms, 3 beautifully appointed bathrooms. A 2-car garage provides ample space for parking and storage. Step inside and be greeted by the warm, inviting ambiance created by the laminate flooring and a cozy fireplace in the living room, perfect for relaxing evenings. The kitchen has new backsplash, also beautiful stone countertops, and modern appliances. The master bathroom has been remodeled. Enjoy the convenience of an upper-level laundry room, making laundry day a breeze. This townhome is nestled in a vibrant community, close to shopping centers. Plus, it's conveniently located near the interstate, making your daily commute a breeze. This townhome offers a comfortable and modern lifestyle in an ideal location. Whether you're looking to entertain friends and family or enjoy some quiet moments by the fireplace, this home has it all. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours!
